ServiceNow ODBC driver.

1. Download and install Java
2. Creation of a ServiceNOW user with odbc role to query data from Power Bi
3. Download the odbc drivers setup file from ServiceNow store.
4. Installation of ODBC driver on system
5. Configuration of data source/DSN in ODBC console
6. Connect from PowerBI



In PowerBi-

1. Go to Get Data-> Search ODBC-> Give sql query
2. Give ODBC CREDS.
